metadata.name: Skyward Divisions
metadata.description:
This image titled "Skyward Divisions" is a photo I took on the fourth evening of my backpacking trip. At sunset, the sky's color split in two, half blue, half pink. It created an otherworldly frame for a photograph and was one of the most beautiful sunsets I have ever witnessed.

"Western Worlds" is a collection of photographs I took on a trip out to Utah last summer. The landscape changed so often that each photo feels like a snapshot from a different world.
